/* eslint-disable */
import * as React from "react";
import { getOverrideProps } from "@aws-amplify/ui-react/internal";
import { Button, Text, View } from "@aws-amplify/ui-react";
export default function FormularioLoginMobile(props) {
  const { login, overrides, ...rest } = props;
  return (
    <View
      width="390px"
      height="600px"
      display="block"
      gap="unset"
      alignItems="unset"
      justifyContent="unset"
      position="relative"
      padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"
      {...getOverrideProps(overrides, "FormularioLoginMobile")}
      {...rest}
    >
      <Text
        fontFamily="Inter"
        fontSize="20px"
        fontWeight="400"
        color="rgba(0,44,133,1)"
        lineHeight="30px"
        textAlign="left"
        display="block"
        direction="column"
        justifyContent="unset"
        width="388.91px"
        height="72.17px"
        gap="unset"
        alignItems="unset"
        position="absolute"
        top="11.93%"
        bottom="76.05%"
        left="0%"
        right="0.28%"
        padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"
        whiteSpace="pre-wrap"
        children="Ingresa tu usuario y contraseña para iniciar sesión"
        {...getOverrideProps(
          overrides,
          "Ingresa tu usuario y contrase\u00F1a para iniciar sesi\u00F3n"
        )}
      ></Text>
      <Button
        width="unset"
        height="35.54px"
        position="absolute"
        top="91.67%"
        bottom="2.41%"
        left="calc(50% - 105px - -47px)"
        size="small"
        isDisabled={false}
        variation="link"
        children="Registrarte aquí"
        {...getOverrideProps(overrides, "Button")}
      ></Button>
      <Text
        fontFamily="Inter"
        fontSize="20px"
        fontWeight="400"
        color="rgba(0,44,133,1)"
        lineHeight="30px"
        textAlign="left"
        display="block"
        direction="column"
        justifyContent="unset"
        width="388.91px"
        height="72.17px"
        gap="unset"
        alignItems="unset"
        position="absolute"
        top="87.11%"
        bottom="0.86%"
        left="0.28%"
        right="0%"
        padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"
        whiteSpace="pre-wrap"
        children="Recuerda que si aún no tienes una cuenta puedes "
        {...getOverrideProps(
          overrides,
          "Recuerda que si a\u00FAn no tienes una cuenta puedes"
        )}
      ></Text>
      <Text
        fontFamily="Inter"
        fontSize="24px"
        fontWeight="600"
        color="rgba(0,44,133,1)"
        lineHeight="30px"
        textAlign="left"
        display="block"
        direction="column"
        justifyContent="unset"
        width="388.91px"
        height="72.17px"
        gap="unset"
        alignItems="unset"
        position="absolute"
        top="0%"
        bottom="87.97%"
        left="0.28%"
        right="0%"
        padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"
        whiteSpace="pre-wrap"
        children="Hola, nos da mucho gusto que estés aquí"
        {...getOverrideProps(
          overrides,
          "Hola, nos da mucho gusto que est\u00E9s aqu\u00ED"
        )}
      ></Text>
      <View
        padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"
        width="385px"
        height="308px"
        display="block"
        gap="unset"
        alignItems="unset"
        justifyContent="unset"
        position="absolute"
        top="176px"
        left="4px"
        {...getOverrideProps(overrides, "Formulario")}
      >
        <View
          width="385px"
          height="308px"
          display="block"
          gap="unset"
          alignItems="unset"
          justifyContent="unset"
          position="absolute"
          top="0px"
          left="0px"
          padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"
          children={login}
          {...getOverrideProps(overrides, "Frame 438")}
        ></View>
      </View>
    </View>
  );
}
